To start an Urban Terror Quake3 server, add this to your /etc/rc.conf:

	quake3server="YES"
	quake3server_flags="+set fs_game ut +set dedicated 1
			    +exec ut.cfg &"

You will need to create a custom ut.cfg file, and place it in
${Q3MODDIR}.

===========================================================================
